# 📦 Requirements

The project was developed and tested in a Linux environment using Python and RDKit.

## Required Dependencies

```text
rdkit
numpy
```

---

# 💻 Running the Project

Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/sobia-naaz/RDKit-Internal-Coordinates.git
```

Move into the project directory:

```bash
cd RDKit-Internal-Coordinates
```

Install dependencies:

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Run the script:

```bash
python internal_coordinates.py
```
